<subSubSection pageId="6" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1010,1518,1544]" box="[151,1010,1518,1544]" pageId="6">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,1010,1518,1544]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="6" reason="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,1010,1518,1544]" pageId="6">
<taxonomicName authority="Ludwig, 1889" authorityName="Ludwig" authorityYear="1889" box="[151,571,1518,1544]" class="Holothuroidea" family="Holothuriidae" genus="Holothuria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aspidochirotida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="bataviae">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,394,1518,1544]" italics="true" pageId="6">Holothuria bataviae</emphasis>
Ludwig, 
<number box="[512,571,1518,1544]" pageId="6" value="1889.0">1889</number>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Ludwig, 1891" authorityName="Ludwig" authorityYear="1891" box="[632,1010,1518,1544]" class="Holothuroidea" family="Holothuriidae" genus="Holothuria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aspidochirotida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="kurti">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[632,834,1518,1544]" italics="true" pageId="6">Holothuria kurti</emphasis>
Ludwig, 
<number box="[951,1010,1518,1544]" pageId="6" value="1891.0">1891</number>
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,1589,1978]" pageId="6">
Unfortunately, Ludwig introduced two 
<emphasis box="[619,772,1590,1613]" italics="true" pageId="6">nomina nova</emphasis>
for 
<taxonomicName authority="Sluiter, 1889" authorityName="Sluiter" authorityYear="1889" box="[833,1232,1589,1614]" class="Holothuroidea" family="Holothuriidae" genus="Holothuria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aspidochirotida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="lamperti">
<emphasis box="[833,1067,1589,1614]" italics="true" pageId="6">Holothuria lamperti</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Sluiter" box="[1081,1232,1589,1614]" pageId="6" refString="Sluiter, C. P. (1889) Nachtragliches uber die Echinodermen Fauna des Java-Meeres. Natuurkundig Tijdschrift voor Nederlandsch-Indie, 49 [1890], 105 - 110, 1 pl. [= Natuurkundig Tijdschrift voor Nederlandsch-Indie (8 th Serie), 10]" type="journal article" year="1889">
Sluiter, 
<number box="[1176,1232,1590,1614]" pageId="6" value="1889.0">1889</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
[non 
<taxonomicName authority="Ludwig, 1886" authorityName="Ludwig" authorityYear="1886" class="Holothuroidea" family="Holothuriidae" genus="Holothuria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aspidochirotida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="lamperti">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6">Holothuria lamperti</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Ludwig" box="[253,425,1625,1650]" pageId="6" refString="Ludwig, H. (1886 a) Die von G. Chierchia auf der Fahrt der Kgl. Ital. Corvette &quot; Vettor Pisani &quot; gesammelten Holothurien. Zoologische Jahrbucher. Zeitschrift fur Systematik, Geographie und Biologie der Thiere, 2 (II), 1 - 36, pls. I - II." type="journal article" year="1886" yearSuffix="a">
Ludwig, 
<number box="[354,412,1625,1650]" pageId="6" value="1886.0">1886</number>
a
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
] (see 
<tableCitation box="[491,575,1625,1650]" captionStart="TABLE 3" captionStartId="7.[151,239,152,175]" captionText="TABLE 3. Pagination of the taxa introduced in Ludwig's Die Seewalzen (1889 – 1892)." pageId="6">
Table 
<number box="[559,575,1626,1650]" pageId="6" value="3.0">3</number>
</tableCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="6" type="reference_group">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,1589,1978]" pageId="6">
<taxonomicName box="[199,428,1661,1686]" class="Holothuroidea" family="Holothuriidae" genus="Holothuria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aspidochirotida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="bataviae">
<emphasis box="[199,428,1661,1686]" italics="true" pageId="6">Holothuria bataviae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was erected by Ludwig on page 
<number box="[809,851,1662,1686]" pageId="6" value="174.0">174</number>
(footnote) (= fascicles 
<number box="[1119,1132,1661,1686]" pageId="6" value="5.0">5</number>
/ 
<number box="[1140,1154,1661,1686]" pageId="6" value="6.0">6</number>
of Ludwig 
<date box="[1290,1412,1662,1686]" pageId="6" value="1889" valueMax="1892">
<number box="[1290,1412,1662,1686]" pageId="6" value="1890.5" valueMax="1892.0" valueMin="1889.0">1889-1892</number>
</date>
= Ludwig 
<number box="[249,309,1698,1722]" pageId="6" value="1889.0">1889</number>
), but is probably a 
<emphasis box="[543,716,1698,1722]" italics="true" pageId="6">forgotten name</emphasis>
since it is missing for instance in the 
<taxonomicName box="[1174,1402,1697,1722]" class="Holothuroidea" family="Molpadiidae" genus="Ankyroderma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Molpadida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="subSpecies" species="annotated" subSpecies="catalogue">annotated catalogue</taxonomicName>
of Holothuroidea by 
<bibRefCitation author="Smiley" box="[355,638,1733,1758]" pageId="6" refString="Smiley, S. &amp; Pawson, D. L. (1991) An annotated catalogue of the holothurians. [Unpublished manuscript]. Institute of Arctic Biology, Fairbanks, Alas. &amp; National Museum of Natural History, Washington, D. C., 184 pp." type="book" year="1991">
Smiley &amp; Pawson (
<number box="[572,630,1734,1758]" pageId="6" value="1991.0">1991</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
or in the 
<emphasis box="[745,1122,1733,1758]" italics="true" pageId="6">World Register of Marine Species</emphasis>
. However, 
<taxonomicName box="[1252,1436,1733,1758]" class="Holothuroidea" family="Holothuriidae" genus="Holothuria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aspidochirotida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="kurti">
<emphasis box="[1252,1436,1733,1758]" italics="true" pageId="6">Holothuria kurti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(introduced by Ludwig in a footnote on page 
<number box="[666,708,1770,1794]" pageId="6" value="329.0">329</number>
= fascicle 
<number box="[833,860,1770,1794]" pageId="6" value="13.0">13</number>
/ 
<number box="[869,897,1770,1794]" pageId="6" value="14.0">14</number>
of Ludwig 
<date box="[1031,1152,1770,1794]" pageId="6" value="1889" valueMax="1892">
<number box="[1031,1152,1770,1794]" pageId="6" value="1890.5" valueMax="1892.0" valueMin="1889.0">1889-1892</number>
</date>
= Ludwig 
<number box="[1279,1335,1769,1794]" pageId="6" value="1891.0">1891</number>
b) on the other hand gained acceptance to replace 
<taxonomicName authority="Sluiter" authorityName="Sluiter" box="[607,916,1805,1830]" class="Holothuroidea" family="Holothuriidae" genus="Holothuria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aspidochirotida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="lamperti">
<emphasis box="[607,833,1805,1830]" italics="true" pageId="6">Holothuria lamperti</emphasis>
Sluiter
</taxonomicName>
(e.g., 
<bibRefCitation author="Meissner" box="[987,1156,1805,1830]" pageId="6" refString="Meissner, M. (1895) Bericht uber die wissenschaftlichen Leistungen in der Naturgeschichte der Echinodermen wahrend des Jahres 1891. Archiv fur Naturgeschichte, 58 (II) [3], 115 - 150." type="journal article" year="1895">
Meissner 
<number box="[1097,1156,1805,1830]" pageId="6" value="1895.0">1895</number>
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Koehler" box="[1168,1431,1805,1830]" pageId="6" refString="Koehler, R. &amp; Vaney, C. (1908) An account of the littoral Holothurioidea collected by the Royal Indian Marine Survey Ship Investigator / Holothuries recueillies par l'Investigator dans l'Ocean Indien. II. Les Holothuries littorales. In: Echinoderma of the Indian Museum. Holothurioidea. Trustees of the Indian Museum, Calcutta, iv + 54 pp., 3 pls. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 1730" type="book" year="1908">
Koehler &amp; Vaney 
<number box="[1372,1431,1806,1830]" pageId="6" value="1908.0">1908</number>
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Sluiter" box="[151,294,1841,1866]" pageId="6" refString="Sluiter, C. P. (1914) Die von Dr. P. N. van Kampen, wahrend seiner Fahrten mit dem Regierungsdampfer &quot; Gier &quot;, 1906 - 1909, im Indischen Archipel gesammelten Holothurien. Contributions a la faune des Indes Neerlandaises, 1 (1), 1 - 28, 1 pl." type="journal article" year="1914">
Sluiter 
<number box="[235,294,1842,1866]" pageId="6" value="1914.0">1914</number>
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Samyn" box="[308,524,1841,1866]" pageId="6" refString="Samyn, Y., Kerr, A., O'Loughlin, M., Massin, C., Pawson, D. L., Rowe, F. W. E., Smiley, S., Solis-Marin, F., Thandar, A. S., VandenSpiegel, D. &amp; Paulay, G. (2010) Using sea cucumbers to illustrate the basics of zoological nomenclature. SPC Beche-de-mer Information Bulletin, 30, 33 - 40." type="journal article" year="2010">
Samyn 
<emphasis box="[395,454,1841,1866]" italics="true" pageId="6">et al.</emphasis>
<number box="[463,524,1842,1866]" pageId="6" value="2010.0">2010</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). Lately Liao Yulin thought that 
<taxonomicName authority="Ludwig, 1891" authorityName="Ludwig" authorityYear="1891" box="[903,1161,1841,1866]" class="Holothuroidea" family="Holothuriidae" genus="Holothuria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aspidochirotida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="kurti">
<emphasis box="[903,992,1841,1866]" italics="true" pageId="6">H. kurti</emphasis>
Ludwig, 
<number box="[1105,1161,1842,1866]" pageId="6" value="1891.0">1891</number>
</taxonomicName>
is probably a young 
<taxonomicName authority="Liao 1980" authorityName="Liao" authorityYear="1980" class="Holothuroidea" family="Holothuriidae" genus="Holothuria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aspidochirotida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="ocellata" subGenus="Theelothuria">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6">H. (Theelothuria) ocellata</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Liao" box="[436,560,1881,1906]" pageId="6" refString="Liao, Yulin (1980) The Aspidochirote holothurians of China with erection of a new genus. In: Jangoux, M. (Ed.), Echinoderms: Present and Past. Proceedings of the European Colloquim on Echinoderms. Brussels / 3 - 8 September 1979. A. A. Balkema, Rotterdam, pp. 115 - 120." type="journal article" year="1980">
Liao 
<number box="[500,560,1881,1905]" pageId="6" value="1980.0">1980</number>
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, other authors placed this species in the subgenus 
<emphasis box="[1165,1346,1881,1906]" italics="true" pageId="6">
H. (
<taxonomicName box="[1211,1338,1881,1906]" class="Holothuroidea" family="Holothuriidae" genus="Holothuria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aspidochirotida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="genus">Holothuria</taxonomicName>
)
</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6">H. (Metriatyla)</emphasis>
(cf. 
<bibRefCitation author="Rowe" box="[348,596,1917,1942]" pageId="6" refString="Rowe, F. W. E. &amp; Gates, J. (1995) Echinodermata. In: Wells, A. (Ed.), Zoological Catalogue of Australia. CSIRO Australia, Melbourne, xiii + 510 pp." type="book" year="1995">
Rowe &amp; Gates 
<number box="[534,596,1917,1942]" pageId="6" value="1995.0">1995</number>
</bibRefCitation>
).] Presently, 
<taxonomicName authority="Ludwig, 1891" authorityName="Ludwig" authorityYear="1891" box="[748,1012,1917,1942]" class="Holothuroidea" family="Holothuriidae" genus="Holothuria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Aspidochirotida" pageId="6" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="kurti">
<emphasis box="[748,839,1917,1942]" italics="true" pageId="6">H. kurti</emphasis>
Ludwig, 
<number box="[956,1012,1917,1941]" pageId="6" value="1891.0">1891</number>
</taxonomicName>
is considered to be a species of 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6">H. (Theelothuria)</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Paulay" box="[328,488,1953,1978]" pageId="6" refString="Paulay, G. (2014 b) Holothuria (Theelothuria) kurti Ludwig, 1891. Available from: World Register of Marine Species at http: // www. marinespecies. org / aphia. php? p = taxdetails &amp; id = 724874 (accessed date 0 3 2015)." type="journal article" year="2014" yearSuffix="b">
Paulay 
<number box="[413,473,1953,1978]" pageId="6" value="2014.0">2014</number>
b
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
